<item>
            <title>[LU-18910] kernel update [RHEL 9.5 5.14.0-503.38.1.el9_5]</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18910</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Security Fix(es) in kernel 5.14.0-503.35.1.el9_5:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;kernel: md: fix deadlock between mddev_suspend and flush bio (CVE-2024-43855)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://access.redhat.com/errata/product/479/ver=/rhel---9/x86_64/RHSA-2025:3506&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://access.redhat.com/errata/product/479/ver=/rhel---9/x86_64/RHSA-2025:3506&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Security Fix(es) in kernel 5.14.0-503.38.1.el9_5:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;kernel: ALSA: usb-audio: Fix out of bounds reads when finding clock sources (CVE-2024-53150)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://access.redhat.com/errata/product/479/ver=/rhel---9/x86_64/RHSA-2025:3937&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://access.redhat.com/errata/product/479/ver=/rhel---9/x86_64/RHSA-2025:3937&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
